ntagonist valsartan on the angiotensin II-renin feedback interruption. <i>Journal of the American Society of Nephrology : JASN</i> 15(12) 3126–3133. DOI:<a href=&quot;https://doi.org/10.1097/01.ASN.0000146686.35541.29&quot;>10.1097/01.ASN.0000146686.35541.29</a>  PUBMED:<a href=&quot;https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15579516/&quot;>https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15579516</a></p></li></ol></body></html>",
